metadata.name: Crazy Stuffed Bunnie #596
metadata.description: The collection consists of 10,000 randomly generated items made up of different colors, styles, accessories and types. that exists on the Ethereum Blockchain. Each CSB Holder will have access to a members area and will earn 1000 CSB Coins to use within the website and boost their publications and profiles on social networks and do the same with the social networks of the other holders. Thus generating an impulse network with 10,000 members. A crazy stuffed bunnies might not pose any threat, but try to tackle 10k and you'll see the difference! Visit www.crazystuffedbunnies.online to learn more.
